            <p>Customer relationships are the foundation of every successful business. Managing leads, tracking customers, and improving sales can become difficult without the right system.</p>

            <p>This is where CRM comes in. CRM helps businesses manage customer interactions, track leads, and improve sales efficiency in one centralized platform.</p>

            <p>A solution like DivineCRM enables businesses to organize customer data, manage sales pipelines, and improve follow-ups — all from one place.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- What is CRM -->
        <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section-tag">Overview</div>
            <h2 class="art-h2">What is CRM?</h2>

            <p class="art-p">CRM stands for Customer Relationship Management. It is software that helps businesses manage customer relationships and sales processes.</p>

            <ul class="art-list">
                <li>Manage customer information</li>
                <li>Track leads and opportunities</li>
                <li>Improve sales follow-ups</li>
                <li>Monitor team performance</li>
                <li>Increase customer satisfaction</li>
                <li>Close deals faster</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Need CRM -->
        <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section-tag">Why CRM</div>
            <h2 class="art-h2">Why Businesses Need CRM</h2>

            <p class="art-p">Many businesses still use Excel sheets or notebooks, which leads to confusion and missed opportunities.</p>

            <div class="art-compare">
                <div class="art-comp-card bad">
                    <div class="art-comp-title">Without CRM</div>
                    <ul class="art-comp-list">
                        <li><span class="xi">✗</span> Leads get missed</li>
                        <li><span class="xi">✗</span> Follow-ups delayed</li>
                        <li><span class="xi">✗</span> Scattered data</li>
                        <li><span class="xi">✗</span> No visibility</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="art-comp-card good">
                    <div class="art-comp-title">With CRM</div>
                    <ul class="art-comp-list">
                        <li><span class="ci">✓</span> Leads tracked</li>
                        <li><span class="ci">✓</span> Automated follow-ups</li>
                        <li><span class="ci">✓</span> Centralized data</li>
                        <li><span class="ci">✓</span> Better performance</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

